OL,6,FHis niece Lynne Lambert said: "They
OL,7,Fweren't experienced soldiers at all.
OL,8,FJust young men who found themselves in
OL,9,Fthis awful situation fighting for
OL,10,Ftheir lives and fighting for freedom
OL,11,Fin a country so far away.
OL,13,F"It must have been absolutely horrific
OL,14,Ffor them and I think they really
OL,15,Fdeserve to be remembered. It really
OL,16,Faffected their lives so personally.
OL,17,FThey weren't the same people when they
OL,18,Fcame back as they were when they left."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
