OL,6,FThe British were eventually forced to
OL,7,Fretreat, but their battle bought the
OL,8,FUN forces crucial time to regroup and
OL,9,Fprotect Seoul from communist attack.
OL,11,FMore than 1,000 men of the British
OL,12,F29th Brigade died and the
OL,13,FGloucestershire Regiment bore the
OL,14,Fbrunt with 620 soldiers killed,
OL,15,Fwounded, or missing.
OL,17,FSo great was their sacrifice that the
OL,18,Fsite was later renamed Gloster Hill
OL,19,Fand a memorial was erected in honour
OL,20,Fof those who fought.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
