OL,6,FPlans for a memorial in the Forest of
OL,7,FDean
OL,9,FThere are now plans for a special
OL,10,Fmemorial closer to home - in the Cyril
OL,11,FHart arboretum in the Forest of Dean.
OL,13,FRoger Deeks, the vice lord-lieutenant
OL,14,Fof Gloucestershire, said these
OL,15,Fveterans have been "somewhat forgotten
OL,16,Ffor a long time" here in the UK.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
