OL,6,FHe said: "The last veteran - Roy Mills
OL,7,F- was still alive when we started the
OL,8,Fproject. He died very sadly five weeks
OL,9,Fago so now they've all gone, the ones
OL,10,Fwho lived in the Forest.
OL,12,F"That becomes a really important time
OL,13,Fto remember them and to have a
OL,14,Fmemorial where young people can come
OL,15,Fand learn about the sacrifices they
OL,16,Fmade."
OL,18,FRoy was 20 when he was deployed. He
OL,19,Fdied on 14 October this year at the
OL,20,Fage of 92. His family is now backing
OL,21,Fthe campaign for a memorial.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
