OL,6,FHe said: "In a few years, many of us
OL,7,Fwon't be here but if we've got this
OL,8,Fbeautiful memorial in this beautiful
OL,9,Fsetting here, in one of the oldest
OL,10,Farboretums in the country... We need
OL,11,Fthe funding and it's so important that
OL,12,Fwe've done it."
OL,14,FLynne said: "We really need to do them
OL,15,Fjustice and have a place where they
OL,16,Fcan be remembered. It's part of our
OL,17,Fhistory."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
